description: $ordi is the first token deployed on the BRC-20 Protocol, now all valid mint inscriptions supported by ORC-CASH as Cash Bills. ORC-CASH protocol allows valid Mint inscriptions to be traded as the tokens themselves, just like cash bills with a serial number. All Mint inscriptions included in this collection will always be valid in the ORC-CASH Indexers until they are sent to a Burn Wallet address which will take them out of circulation.
name: ordi (ORC-CASH)
